    "These results provide guidance to other open-source platforms, such as to provide the community with the platform-specific LLM to stimulate community participation and output.",
    "Another key implication concerns the extent to which LLMs are effective in software development tasks.",
    "Most research, including Peng et al. (2023), notes that LLMs enhance an individual's ability to complete guided tasks.",
    "These experimental programming tasks can be viewed as capability tasks, where developers generate a solution from scratch.",
    "However, our findings indicate that LLMs are more effective for iterative tasks, where understanding existing work is necessary before making their contribution in the current iteration."
